  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Odisha</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Odisha has three seasons: hot summer (March–June), monsoon (July–September) and a pleasant winter (October–February). October to February is ideal — the Rath Yatra falls in June/July, Konark is best in winter light, the Chilika Lake flamingos arrive in November and the olive ridley turtles nest from November to March.</p>
